arts.ttl: Highligted: Heracles Almelo can build on a strong run
arts.sum: This season, Heracles has lost only two of the thirteen home games, against top clubs PSV and Ajax. With three wins in the TOTO KNVB Cup and five Eredivisie matches unbeaten (one win, four draws), the Heraclieden have gone eight games unbeaten.

arts.ttl: Preview: Heracles vs. Go Ahead Eagles - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Saturday's Eredivisie clash between Heracles and Go Ahead Eagles, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
